data.description: LIKE NEW! 2020 Empire Communities Home. Gorgeous curb appeal w/ low maintenance lawn care for effortless living. Residents of Coastal Point enjoy fantastic amenities, including access to the renowned CCISD schools w/ Education Village bus stop, resort-style community pool, clubhouse, park & trails. The sought-after Victoria split & open floorplan features a tiled entry, high ceilings & abundant natural light. At the entry find a versatile study w/ French doors & 1st bed & private bath, ideal for guests. The heart of the home is the perfect entertaining space, seamlessly connecting the well-equipped kitchen w/ trendy gray cabinetry, granite counters & walk-in pantry to the enormous dining & living. Privately located primary oasis is spacious & offers dual vanities, tub, separate shower & an oversized walk-in closet. 2 additional bedrooms share a double sink full bath, while the charming backyard & covered patio w/ ceiling fan offer the ideal setting for outdoor relaxation & gatherings.
